---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Audit Request Received | Designed by Anthony"
  description="Your free website audit request has been received. Anthony will review your submission and reach out within 24 hours."
  hideBreadcrumbs={true}
  hidePreFooterCTA={true}
  noindex={true}
>
  <section class="section-shell thank-you-shell">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="surface-card thank-you-card">
        <div class="thank-you-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="icon" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-tag">Audit Requested</div>
        <h1>Audit request received.</h1>
        <p class="thank-you-lead">Anthony will review your submission and reach out within 24 hours with the clearest next step.</p>

        <h2 class="thank-you-expect-heading">What to expect in the next 24 hours</h2>

        <div class="thank-you-steps">
          <div class="thank-step">
            <span class="thank-step-number">01</span>
            <div>
              <h2>I review the site</h2>
              <p>I check speed, mobile experience, Google visibility, and whether the site makes it easy for people to call.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="thank-step">
            <span class="thank-step-number">02</span>
            <div>
              <h2>I spot the biggest issue</h2>
              <p>I find the biggest thing keeping the phone from ringing and tell you how to fix it.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="thank-step">
            <span class="thank-step-number">03</span>
            <div>
              <h2>I send the next move</h2>
              <p>You will hear from Anthony within 24 hours with a practical reply, not a vague pitch deck or automated sequence.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="thank-you-while-you-wait">
          <p class="thank-you-wait-label">While you wait</p>
          <p>Most audits are delivered same-day. The 24-hour window is the outer limit, not the norm. In the meantime, these will help you get more out of the report when it arrives:</p>
          <div class="thank-you-reads">
            <a href="/blog/contractor-website-mistakes" class="surface-card thank-you-read-card">
              <span class="card-tag">Trust</span>
              <span>5 Things Wrong With Most Contractor Websites</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/blog/site-speed-conversion" class="surface-card thank-you-read-card">
              <span class="card-tag">Performance</span>
              <span>How Site Speed Impacts Revenue</span>
            </a>
            <a href="/blog/mobile-first-seo" class="surface-card thank-you-read-card">
              <span class="card-tag">Mobile</span>
              <span>Mobile-First SEO Is the Only SEO That Matters Now</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="thank-you-direct">
          <p>Need to add more context before I reply?</p>
          <div class="thank-you-links">
            <a href="/contact">Use the contact form</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="thank-you-actions">
          <a href="/portfolio" class="btn btn-primary">See Example Builds</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">Explore Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .thank-you-shell {
    min-height: 70vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .thank-you-card {
    width: min(860px, 100%);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .thank-you-icon {
    width: 84px;
    height: 84px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.14);
  }

  .thank-you-icon .icon {
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .thank-you-card h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.05em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    margin: 1rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .thank-you-lead {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-gray);
    font-size: 1.08rem;
  }

  .thank-you-expect-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.8vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-cream);
  }

  .thank-you-steps {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .thank-step {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
    padding: 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: rgba(8, 15, 28, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }

  .thank-step-number {
    width: 2rem;
    height: 2rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.24);
    color: #bfdbfe;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .thank-step h2 {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .thank-step p,
  .thank-you-direct p {
    color: var(--text-gray);
  }

  .thank-you-while-you-wait {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .thank-you-wait-label {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: #93c5fd;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .thank-you-while-you-wait > p:nth-child(2) {
    color: var(--text-gray);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .thank-you-reads {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .thank-you-read-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-white);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition: border-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .thank-you-read-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3);
  }

  .thank-you-direct {
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .thank-you-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
  }

  .thank-you-links a {
    color: var(--text-white);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .thank-you-actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .thank-you-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.25rem;
    }

    .thank-step {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .thank-you-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
